summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 6232, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of the alley in Block one (1) of Maynard's Plat of the Town, now City of Seattle, by grading and planking the same, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment," under the provisions of Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
